snippet.title: VENGE 2.0 - Release Date Trailer [ EMERGENCY ALERT ]
snippet.description:
YOU ARE IN DANGER.
THIS IS NOT A DRILL.
Stay Safe...

Venge: https://bit.ly/getVenge
Discord: https://discord.gg/q4c6VVfmMB
Patreon: https://patreon.com/Ekrcoaster

Venge 2.0 is finally coming out! Venge is a fantasy horror game set in a flipped parallel universe. 
You'll be sucked in and fight terrifying monsters while you make choices and escape to freedom. Act 2 development should start soon after!
